{"tid":2335994,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"上訴庭駁回郭卓堅挑戰立法會修改議事規則上訴申請 下令支付雙方訟費","createTime":"2020-12-22T09:36:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T10:37:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"51b3c87af04ea5b0bb3968b22cd8116e506437ea","tid":2335994,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"高等法院上訴庭駁回長洲居民郭卓堅，就有關挑戰立法會修改《議事規則》的上訴申請。<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅3年前入稟高等法院，挑戰立法會修改《議事規則》，將立法會全體委員會會議的最低法定人數，由全體委員的一半減至20名委員，去年被裁定敗訴。<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅今日到高等法院上訴庭申請上訴，政府指入稟人的論點並無法律依據，而且他並非立法會一員，促請法庭拒絕其許可申請。上訴庭駁回他的上訴許可申請，擇日頒布書面理由。<br />\n<br />\n法庭下令郭卓堅支付立法會及律政司雙方訟費。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566626-20201222.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566626-20201222.htm&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=7d598a5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566626-20201222.htm&h=f847c93c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566626-20201222.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ed30f2795e1de6e0679e6c8b23bf3fe119219e16","tid":2335994,"uid":263648,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51b3c87af04ea5b0bb3968b22cd8116e506437ea","tid":2335994,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"高等法院上訴庭駁回長洲居民郭卓堅，就有關挑戰立法會修改《議事規則》的上訴申請。<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅3年前入稟高等法院，挑戰立法會修改《議事規則》，將立法會全體委員會會議的最低法定人數，由全體委員的一半減至20名委員，去年被裁定敗訴。<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅今日到高等法院上訴庭申請上訴，政府指入稟人的論點並無法律依據，而且他並非立法會一員，促請法庭拒絕其許可申請。上訴庭駁回他的上訴許可申請，擇日頒布書面理由。<br />\n<br />\n法庭下令郭卓堅支付立法會及律政司雙方訟費。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566626-20201222.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566626-20201222.htm&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=7d598a5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566626-20201222.htm&h=f847c93c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566626-20201222.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:40:44.000Z","msg":"老人家既堅持抗爭精神，令人佩服。"},{"pid":"35f8ebe52e1ee8b2a2f55ae935463b9ed943ba08","tid":2335994,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T09:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80570d24ece1f28a05bec59faf28b3e14500964a","tid":2335994,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T10:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最強法律抗爭銀髮手足"},{"pid":"ded5b31cdf90bdc344eb9579baa8778849b6c9ce","tid":2335994,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T10:37:36.000Z","msg":"郭卓堅今日到高等法院上訴庭申請上訴，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">政府指入稟人的論點並無法律依據，而且他並非立法會一員</span></span>，促請法庭拒絕其許可申請<br />\n<br />\n政府又係立法會一員？？"}]}